In a world full of darkness and injustice, the Great King of Lore Ipsum decided to create a tournament. This deadly tournament will decide the new heros that can bring peace to kingdom.\n You, a famous adventurer, hear about this and decide to ask about. A man, working for King Foo, explains that the battle will have 8 parties with three people each, and they'll fight till death.\n Hearing this, you decided to join the Great Colossal Century Magic Tournament For The Peace of Mankind in This World Full of Darkness First Edition (a.k.a. GCCMTFTPoMiTWFoDFE) with another two friends.
